3#ifndef __NVKM_MMU_H__
4#define __NVKM_MMU_H__
5#include <core/subdev.h>
6#include <core/mm.h>
7struct nvkm_device;
8struct nvkm_mem;
9
10#define NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_SIZE 4096
11#define NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_MASK (NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_SIZE - 1)
12#define NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_SHIFT 12
13#define NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_ALIGN(a) (((a) + NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_MASK) & ~NOUVEAU_GPU_PAGE_MASK)
14
15struct nvkm_vm_pgt {
16 struct nvkm_memory *mem[2];
17 u32 refcount[2];
18};
19
20struct nvkm_vm_pgd {
21 struct list_head head;
22 struct nvkm_gpuobj *obj;
23};
24
25struct nvkm_vma {
26 struct list_head head;
27 int refcount;
28 struct nvkm_vm *vm;
29 struct nvkm_mm_node *node;
30 u64 offset;
31 u32 access;
32};
33
34struct nvkm_vm {
35 struct nvkm_mmu *mmu;
36
37 struct mutex mutex;
38 struct nvkm_mm mm;
39 struct kref refcount;
40
41 struct list_head pgd_list;
42 atomic_t engref[NVKM_SUBDEV_NR];
43
44 struct nvkm_vm_pgt *pgt;
45 u32 fpde;
46 u32 lpde;
47};
48
49int nvkm_vm_new(struct nvkm_device *, u64 offset, u64 length, u64 mm_offset,
50 struct lock_class_key *, struct nvkm_vm **);
51int nvkm_vm_ref(struct nvkm_vm *, struct nvkm_vm **, struct nvkm_gpuobj *pgd);
52int nvkm_vm_boot(struct nvkm_vm *, u64 size);
53int nvkm_vm_get(struct nvkm_vm *, u64 size, u32 page_shift, u32 access,
54 struct nvkm_vma *);
55void nvkm_vm_put(struct nvkm_vma *);
56void nvkm_vm_map(struct nvkm_vma *, struct nvkm_mem *);
57void nvkm_vm_map_at(struct nvkm_vma *, u64 offset, struct nvkm_mem *);
58void nvkm_vm_unmap(struct nvkm_vma *);
59void nvkm_vm_unmap_at(struct nvkm_vma *, u64 offset, u64 length);
60
61struct nvkm_mmu {
62 const struct nvkm_mmu_func *func;
63 struct nvkm_subdev subdev;
64
65 u64 limit;
66 u8 dma_bits;
67 u8 lpg_shift;
68};
69
70int nv04_mmu_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_mmu **);
71int nv41_mmu_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_mmu **);
72int nv44_mmu_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_mmu **);
73int nv50_mmu_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_mmu **);
74int gf100_mmu_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_mmu **);
75#endif
